WEBVTT

00:02:29.369 --> 00:02:31.488
I think tonight's probably
a good first step

00:02:31.512 --> 00:02:33.805
to get people to think about fundraising

00:02:33.829 --> 00:02:36.258
more as an opportunity

00:02:36.282 --> 00:02:38.170
and less as a dirty word.

00:02:38.953 --> 00:02:42.200
If you want to change the world,
you have to know how to pay for it.

00:02:42.224 --> 00:02:43.414
To do that well,

00:02:43.438 --> 00:02:45.414
you have to understand three big things.

00:02:45.438 --> 00:02:48.175
Your feelings about wealth and money,

00:02:48.199 --> 00:02:50.692
the importance of building relationships,

00:02:50.716 --> 00:02:52.916
and how to ask for what you want.

00:02:53.303 --> 00:02:56.296
Let's start at the top,
your feelings about wealth and money.

00:02:56.320 --> 00:02:58.907
What is your relationship to money?

00:02:58.931 --> 00:03:00.622
Money is complicated,